casebody.data:
ILLINOIS, petitioner,
v.
Derrick A. CUMMINGS. No. 14-209. Supreme Court of the United States April 27, 2015.

Opinion

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. On petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Illinois. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Supreme Court of Illinois for further consideration in light of Rodriguez v. United States, 575 U.S. ----, --- S.Ct. ----, --- L.E.2d ---- (2015).
